"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89ecff565fa977216521c84e28a6bc6c83a1a0a","tid":1629213,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"19bca7dafb8b364a0d29d1cf4f3e37244eaffaa9","tid":1629213,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2607a33dba3c778e02a5ff4a5752d71da5231f85","tid":1629213,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"grammar 錯既英文就算9數啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"Grammar錯有咩問題？明咪得"},{"pid":"8634db7f67c84da8941923ed6de46a6eb787e556","tid":1629213,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19bca7dafb8b364a0d29d1cf4f3e37244eaffaa9","tid":1629213,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2607a33